de.unistuttgart.vis.wearable.os.handle

Class APIHandle

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper
        • android.app.Application
          • de.unistuttgart.vis.wearable.os.handle.APIHandle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2

    public class APIHandle
extends android.app.Application
    Kernel API Handle that shall be implemented in all apps using the garment sdk. This class tries to connect the application to the garment kernel service allowing the APIFunctions class to call the kernel apis.
    Author:
    roehrdor
